Chrome extension showing a "page action" (button in omnibar) if humans.txt is
detected. Users can click on the icon to see the humans.txt file.

Install this extension at the Chrome Web Store:
https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/pocdghmbbodjiclginddlaimdaholhfk

# What's humans.txt?

A simple standard to show who's contributed to a website. Participating websites simply put a plain-text file at `/humans.txt`.

For example, [here's Google's humans.txt](https://google.com/humans.txt).
